    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required levels for MRL 2. Six factors appropriately scoped as not-assessed per MRL 2 requirements. Validation evidence demonstrates CFD model predicts hemolysis index within 15% of experimental measurements across all operating points. The relative hemolysis index criterion (RH < 1) is satisfied for all five simulated operating conditions. The model is accepted as sufficiently credible for identifying worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the Class II CPB device.",
